CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Grupo Financiero Galicia SA is a financial service holding company. It provides general banking services, proprietary brand credit card services, personal loans, insurance, and other services. The company's operating business segments are Banks, Ecosistema Naranja X, Insurance, and Other Businesses. It generates maximum revenue from Banks.
